      "text": [
        " أَهْلِ اَلْجِزْيَةِ يُؤْخَذُ مِنْ أَمْوَالِهِمْ وَ مَوَاشِيهِمْ شَيْءٌ سِوَى اَلْجِزْيَةِ قَالَ «لاَ»."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1672 - Muhammad ibn Muslim narrated from Abu Ja’far Imam Muhammad ibn Ali Al-Baqir (as) regarding the People of the jizya:\n\"Is anything other than the jizya taken from their wealth and livestock?\"\nImam (as) replied: \"No.\""
        ]
      }
